  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="KT240-kilavi">varaiviṭai āṟṟāḷ eṉak kavaṉṟa tōḻikkuk kiḻatti uraittatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">Told by HER to the confidante who was anxious she
          wouldn't have the strength [to await] the time of marriage. </p>
      </div>

      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="KT240">
          <l> paṉipputa livarnta paiṅkoṭi yavaraik</l>
          <l> kiḷivā yoppi ṉoḷiviṭu paṉmalar</l>
          <l> verukkuppal luruviṉ mullaiyoṭu kañala</l>
          <l> vāṭai vantataṉ ṟalaiyu nōyporak</l>
          <l> kaṇṭiciṉ vāḻi tōḻi teṇṭiraik</l>
          <l> kaṭalāḻ kalattiṟ ṟōṉṟi</l>
          <l> mālai maṟaiyumavar maṇineṭuṅ kuṉṟē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg xml:lang="en">
          <l>On top of the north wind's coming,</l>
          <l rend="indent">so that the many translucent <note place="foot"><term xml:lang="ta">oḷi
            viṭu</term> : do the blossoms let the light come through, or do they emit light, as a
            slightly circumferential way of expressing that they are bright?</note> blossoms,
            resembling parakeet mouths,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">on the field bean, whose fresh creepers have climbed the dewy shrubs,<note place="foot">Does <term xml:lang="ta">putal</term> refer to the jasmine shrubs?</note>
          </l>
          <l rend="indent">crowd together with the jasmine [buds] formed like the teeth of a wild
            cat,</l>
          <l>so that pain strikes [me] − see, oh friend −</l>
          <l>his long hill, a sapphire, <note place="foot">Cām. takes <term xml:lang="ta">maṇi</term>
            as an attribute to <term xml:lang="ta">kuṉṟu</term> (a hill yielding sapphires), but the
            image is more convincing if it is taken as an apposition (for a parallel attesting such
            a notion see NA 173.6f.: <term xml:lang="ta">maṇiyiṉ tōṉṟum | ammalai kiḻavōṉ</term> ).</note>vanishes in the evening, <note place="foot">Or: "see, oh friend, his long hill, a
            sapphire vanishing in the evening ... ".</note></l>
          <l rend="indent2">appearing like a ship sinking into the sea of clear waves.</l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
